p

p1 <- rotate_tree(p, angle = 0) +

  ggplot2::scale_color_manual(values = pal.alb, na.value = '#000000') +
  guides(colour = "none") 
## Coordinate system already present. Adding new coordinate system, which will

p1

p2 <- p1 + geom_fruit(

  stat = 'identity',
  aes(y = Bin,fill = p), #
  alpha = 0.6,

  geom = geom_bar 
) + 
  scale_fill_manual(values = pal.alb,

                                         )) + legend.theme
